## When You Need to Intervene

### 1. Review Agent Decisions

```bash
# Check recent cases
limacharlie case list --oid {{ org.oid }} --output yaml

# Review a specific case
limacharlie case get --id <case_number> --oid {{ org.oid }} --output yaml
```

### 2. Handle Stuck Cases

```bash
# Manually tag to re-trigger the next agent
limacharlie case update --id <case_number> --add-tag needs-l2-review \
  --oid {{ org.oid }}
```

### 3. Override Agent Containment

```bash
# De-isolate a sensor
limacharlie sensor rejoin --sid <SID> --oid {{ org.oid }}

# Document the override
limacharlie case add-note --id <case_number> --type analysis \
  --content "Manual override: de-isolated sensor. Reason: false positive." \
  --oid {{ org.oid }}
```

### 4. Manually Invoke Specialist Agents

{% for team_key, team in agents.teams.items() %}
{% if team.mentions %}
{% for m in team.mentions %}
```bash
# Request {{ m.agent }}
limacharlie case add-note --id <case_number> --type analysis \
  --content "@{{ m.mention }} <your instructions here>" \
  --oid {{ org.oid }}
```

