## Emergency: Shut Down All Automation

> [!CAUTION]
> Use only if the SOC pipeline is actively misbehaving. This stops **all** automated case processing.

```bash
{% for agent in agents.scheduled %}
limacharlie dr set --name "{{ agent.trigger_rule }}" --enabled false --oid {{ org.oid }}
{% endfor %}
```

To re-enable, set `--enabled true` on each rule.

